---
import Section from './Section.astro'
---

<Section id="problem" title="run one agent and it's easy. run a fleet and you've quietly built a small distributed system.">
  <!-- bento: each failure gets a small animated diagram. decoration only
       (aria-hidden); the base attribute state of every svg is the completed,
       readable picture, so reduced-motion (global 0.01ms kill) and no-JS see
       a sensible static illustration. -->
  <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-lp-border bg-lp-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-lp-muted/40">
      <div class="mb-5 text-lp-muted" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 220 88" class="h-24 w-full" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round">
          <rect x="96" y="22" width="30" height="42" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-lp-fg" opacity=".7" />
          <path d="M103 33h16M103 41h16M103 49h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".4" />
          <circle cx="22" cy="30" r="4" fill="currentColor" class="text-lp-fg" opacity=".8" />
          <path class="pb-read pb-read-a text-lp-fg" d="M32 30 C 56 18, 76 22, 92 32" pathLength="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".7" />
          <circle cx="22" cy="58" r="4" fill="currentColor" opacity=".5" />
          <path class="pb-read pb-read-b" d="M32 58 C 56 70, 76 64, 92 54" pathLength="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".45" />
          <text x="136" y="47" font-size="10" fill="currentColor" opacity=".6" font-family="var(--font-mono)">×2</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-lp-fg">▸ they redo each other's work</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-lp-muted">agent B re-reads every file agent A just read — same greps, same conclusions, tokens burned twice.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-lp-border bg-lp-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-lp-muted/40">
      <div class="mb-5 text-lp-muted" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 220 88" class="h-24 w-full" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round">
          {[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8].map((i) => (
            <rect
              class="pb-cold"
              style={`animation-delay:${i * 0.28}s`}
              x={24 + (i % 3) * 22}
              y={16 + Math.floor(i / 3) * 20}
              width="16"
              height="14"
              rx="2"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              opacity=".45"
            />
          ))}
          <text x="24" y="82" font-size="9" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55" font-family="var(--font-mono)">cold · opens 9</text>
          <rect class="pb-warm text-lp-accent" x="152" y="26" width="20" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <path d="M157 35l3 3 5-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-lp-accent" opacity=".9" />
          <text x="146" y="82" font-size="9" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55" font-family="var(--font-mono)">warm · needs 1</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-lp-fg">▸ they forget everything</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-lp-muted">tomorrow's run re-derives today's context from zero. a cold worker opened 9 files where a warm one needed 1.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-lp-border bg-lp-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-lp-muted/40">
      <div class="mb-5 text-lp-muted" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 220 88" class="h-24 w-full" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round">
          <circle cx="42" cy="38" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-lp-fg" opacity=".7" />
          <path d="M30 58h24M30 65h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".35" />
          <text x="16" y="82" font-size="9" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55" font-family="var(--font-mono)">SessionToken</text>
          <circle cx="178" cy="38" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-lp-fg" opacity=".7" />
          <path d="M166 58h24M166 65h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".35" />
          <text x="158" y="82" font-size="9" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55" font-family="var(--font-mono)">login flow</text>
          <path class="pb-half" d="M52 38 H 96" pathLength="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 4" opacity=".5" />
          <path class="pb-half pb-half-r" d="M168 38 H 124" pathLength="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 4" opacity=".5" />
          <path class="pb-gap" d="M106 33l8 10M114 33l-8 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".6" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-lp-fg">▸ their notes don't connect</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-lp-muted">two findings about the same module sit as unrelated blobs — nothing links SessionToken to the login flow.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-lp-muted">
    and the usual fix makes it worse: you gave each agent its own worktree — and quietly deleted
    the shared state everyone was leaning on.
  </p>
</Section>

<style>
  /* base states are the finished picture; keyframes dip away and return */
  .pb-read {
    stroke-dasharray: 1;
    animation: pb-read 3.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .pb-read-b {
    animation-delay: 1.6s;
  }
  @keyframes pb-read {
    0% { stroke-dashoffset: 1; }
    40%, 75% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    100% { stroke-dashoffset: -1; }
  }
  .pb-cold {
    animation: pb-cold 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pb-cold {
    0%, 20% { opacity: 0.45; }
    8% { opacity: 0.95; }
  }
  .pb-warm {
    animation: pb-warm 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pb-warm {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.55; }
  }
  .pb-half {
    stroke-dasharray: 3 4;
    animation: pb-half 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .pb-half-r {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }
  @keyframes pb-half {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { opacity: 0.15; }
  }
  .pb-gap {
    animation: pb-gap 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pb-gap {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
    50% { opacity: 0.25; }
  }
</style>
